name: Janet Johnson
description: I am an independent, intelligent, honest, optimistic, caring, loyal, pretty , very patient and trustworthy woman. I am very, very difficult to anger and do not like negative energy. There is a lot of energy here and it is all positive, and with the right guy unlimited possibilities in all aspects of our lives. I am a one man woman, and always will be. I am not your average woman definitely not boring, and will always make you laugh.
